div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Visit the island\'s most picturesque spots that would make a perfect addition to your Instagram feed!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_777/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/yjjevheykkwnwdththoa/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"couple in nusa penida\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_777/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/yjjevheykkwnwdththoa/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Round trip hotel transfers and a delicious lunch are also included for a stress-free day</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1024,h_768/w_63,x_11,y_11,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/coh7fhjdfv7zmjjin9kv/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"fast boat with klook branding from bali to nusa penida\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1024,h_768/w_63,x_11,y_11,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/coh7fhjdfv7zmjjin9kv/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">You\'ll first take a fast boat from Sanur Harbour to Nusa Penida</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1214,h_764/w_74,x_14,y_14,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/da2jmz5ep0xn0iq8w9fp/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"fast boat with klook branding from bali to nusa penida \" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1214,h_764/w_74,x_14,y_14,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/da2jmz5ep0xn0iq8w9fp/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Have a sail from Sanur Habour to Nusa Penida! If you get motion sickness, it\'s highly recommend you take motion sickness pills before hopping on!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_612/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/lyqrzaueglkae0fxyeyt/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"Nusa Penida Bali\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_612/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/lyqrzaueglkae0fxyeyt/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Embark on a Nusa Penida day trip from Bali and enjoy a full day of adventure and breathtaking views</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_1945/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/hsdzrtjui8sfmrviitsh/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"nature\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_1945/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/hsdzrtjui8sfmrviitsh/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Take signature photo with Kelingking Island as your background</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_1942/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/hvvkr1apiw6frwm84t7w/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"nature\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_1942/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/hvvkr1apiw6frwm84t7w/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Admire the beauty of Nusa Penida in this one-of-a-kind tour from Klook!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1156,h_867/w_71,x_13,y_13,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/xo3cnu8uoe6m0wcrwuea/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"nusa penida tour\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1156,h_867/w_71,x_13,y_13,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/xo3cnu8uoe6m0wcrwuea/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Participants of the tour will be gathered at this Klook meeting point prior to embarking on the fast boat!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1280,h_588/w_79,x_14,y_14,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/v94xjly2wtq4mu8fphvq/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"Nusa Penida Tour snorkeling\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1280,h_588/w_79,x_14,y_14,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/v94xjly2wtq4mu8fphvq/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Experience the diverse marine life of Bali (depends on the weather) during snorkeling activities at Crystal Bay, Manta Bay, or Gamat Bay</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_971/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/dw3dqlrenlsp08cqasgx/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"car charter\" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_971/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/dw3dqlrenlsp08cqasgx/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Enjoy a convenient car transfer!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_971/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/nwbpaevamdz1ywjbafo2/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"Nusa Penida \" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_971/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/nwbpaevamdz1ywjbafo2/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Once you arrive to Nusa Penida, you will arrive at the shore You\'ll need to walk through shallow water to hop off the boat so be sure to wear sandals and you\'ll be picked up by your friendly Klook tour guide and driver for the day.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-image-desc\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"img-container\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><img class=\"v-lazy-logo\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/image/upload/image_logo_mx7wgd.png\" alt=\"logoImg\" data-v-1bf1dec9=\"\"><img class=\"seo-lazy-image\" src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_970/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/kzlpm91mgpcewxd0sbpx/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\" alt=\"Nusa Penida \" data-src=\"https://res.klook.com/images/fl_lossy.progressive,q_65/c_fill,w_1295,h_970/w_80,x_15,y_15,g_south_west,l_Klook_water_br_trans_yhcmh3/activities/kzlpm91mgpcewxd0sbpx/NusaPenidaInstagramTourfromBali.webp\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"page-activity-description-desc page-activity-description-desc-desktop\" data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\"><span data-v-3db8ddd9=\"\">Learn about Nusa Penida from our Klook guides</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"grey_gap\" class=\"experience-section-item grey_gap\">\r\n<div id=\"grey_gap\" class=\"k-section gap  experiences-activity-dto grey_gap\" data-navigation-title=\"\" data-spm-provide=\"section\">\r\n<div id=\"grey_gap\" class=\"divider-gap sec